name: OGT
description: Opengate is an innovative global NFT trading platform based on the Filecoin ecosystem. It is committed to building a NFT market that securely and permanently stores NFT data and is truly decentralized, creating value through exchange and returning profits to the community. And launched a continuous equity incentive ecological model, such as: providing investors with guaranteed repurchase and pledge services, providing rewards for global creators and project teams, etc.
